 <P>Hello Users !!! <br>  
   This STUDENT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM web application is a Dynamic web project tool and has been developed to
 do registeration for students who want to participate in Debate Event during CollegeFest.</P>
 <P>
 This Application can perform the CRUD operations to manage records of the 
  Students Participating in the CollegeFest and keeps track of the  details of  
  participating students based on their course.
 
InOrder to do so it creates a table with the help of Platforms Spring, MVC, Hibernate ORM and 
 performs following CRUD(Create Read Update Delete) operations on the table.<br><br>
1. Insert new student records into the table.<br>
2. Update existing student records into the table.<br>
3. Delete existing student records from the table.<br>
4. Lists/Print all student records from the table<br>
</P>
So You can check all the students who have registered for Debate Event in College Fest and 
add these details for new students who wish to participate. In addition you can also update 
 information of existing students and delete the student records incase they dont want to continue  
 participation in CollegeFest and want to withdraw.<br><br>
  Please click on the link below to proceed to main page and to see the list of participating students<br>
